{
  "stem": "26731.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He could have arrested me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Actually, one of my former classmates got arrested.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They would have put me in the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I hoped to get me out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, who knows what.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Deportation-- you don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You'd rather not find out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He got out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They got him-- actually the-- the boss for the working crew actually went-- [INAUDIBLE] that he was absolutely needed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They couldn't do the demolition without him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was an expert in what have you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He got out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was very lucky, because that particular boss who did it was not very nice to my father.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But since he did that, they overlooked it and nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I wonder what he would have done otherwise.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But OK, it happened, twice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was exceedingly fortunate whatever happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "For instance, when I left the factory one day-- at that time, there were no more lists.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They just grabbed people when they probably needed to.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I don't know how many Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They came around.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The SS came around in trucks, collected everyone at the various factories and transported us to another transition camps.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Crew, Crew was a nightclub.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "These huge halls.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they took out the chairs, tables, and used it as collection.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And there, they brought everyone in, regardless who it was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then, they more or less weeded people out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Let's see who we have got here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Lo and behold, they got-- it was a friend, Gerhardt, we worked together in the factory.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they realized we were both Geltungsjuden.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the guy was quite nice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And said OK, good luck.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I don't want to see you anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Bye-bye, and let us go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Of course, we knew exactly what would happen if we would have stayed there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And there again, bureaucracy.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
